MACERROR(1) User Contributed Perl Documentation MACERROR(1)

NAME

macerror

SYNOPSIS

% macerror -23

DESCRIPTION

The macerror script translates Mac error numbers into their symbolic name and description.

SEE ALSO

Mac::Errors
